{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><i>Once upon a time, a little Slime...</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Summary</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This game consists of leveling up and trying your chance to beat the final boss of the game (<strong><i>or not</i></strong>)...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Story</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Once upon a time, a little Slime who was heading to his best friend's house but when he was arriving, he saw that someone was bothering his friend and decided to intervene...</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Unfortunately for him, the enemy was much stronger than him and ends up losing all his memory in relation to his skills etc... so his friend decides to help him find everything and even learn new skills!</i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Increase your stats by earning and using the &quot;<i><strong>Stat Points</strong></i>&quot;,</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Craft items (E.g.: <i>Craft an &quot;<strong>Angelical Gem</strong>&quot; with a &quot;<strong>Gem Fragment</strong>&quot; and an &quot;<strong>Angel Eye</strong>&quot;</i>),</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Buy new Abilities in the Shop with &quot;<strong><i>Coins</i></strong>&quot; and buy new Auras with &quot;<strong><i>Angelical Gems</i></strong>&quot;,</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Make your own Mods,</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Difficutly</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Green</strong> - <i>Easy</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Blue</strong> - <i>Normal</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Red</strong> - <i>Hard</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>IMPOSSIBLE</strong>:<br><i>You can put any color with the button &quot;<strong>SLIME COL</strong>&quot;.</i></p><